# Catalog/Dictionary Sync Rule

- `config/comprehensive_data_element_list.json` is the canonical source of data elements.
- `docs/DATA-GOVERNANCE/DATA_DICTIONARY.md` must mirror that catalog by source and path coverage.
- Any change to one file requires updating the other in the same change.
- Do not leave one file stale with missing or extra data elements relative to the other.
